quran[13]{c,v,t,f}:
  72,1,"Sọ pé: “Wọ́n fi ìmísí ránṣẹ́ sí mi pé, dájúdájú ìjọ kan nínú àwọn àlùjànnú tẹ́tí (sí al-Ƙur’ān).” Wọ́n sì sọ pé: “Dájúdájú àwa gbọ́ al-Ƙur’ān ìyanu.",""
  72,2,"Ó ń ṣètọ́sọ́nà síbi ìmọ̀nà. Nítorí náà, a gbà á gbọ́. Àwa kò sì níí fi ẹnì kan kan ṣe akẹgbẹ́ fún Olúwa wa (àwa kò níí ṣẹbọ).",""
  72,3,"Àti pé dájúdájú títóbi Olúwa wa ga. Kò fi ẹnì kan kan ṣe aya àti ọmọ.",""
  72,4,"Dájúdájú òmùgọ̀ nínú wa máa ń sọ ìsọkúsọ nípa Allāhu.",""
  72,5,"Dájúdájú àwa sì ń rò pé ènìyàn àti àlùjànnú kò níí pa irọ́ mọ́ Allāhu ni.",""
  72,6,"Àti pé dájúdájú àwọn ọkùnrin kan nínú ènìyàn máa ń fi àwọn ọkùnrin kan nínú àwọn àlùjànnú wá ààbò. Àwọn àlùjànnú sì ṣe àlékún aburú fún wọn.",""
  72,7,"Dájúdájú àwọn àlùjànnú lérò gẹ́gẹ́ bí ẹ̀yin ènìyàn náà ṣe lérò pé, Allāhu kò níí gbé ẹnì kan kan dìde (lẹ́yìn ikú).",""
  72,8,"Dájúdájú àwa wá (ọ̀rọ̀ àyọ́gbọ́) wá sí sánmọ̀, a sì bá a tí ó ti kún fún àwọn ẹ̀ṣọ́ tó lágbára àti àwọn ògúnná.",""
  72,9,"Dájúdájú àwa máa ń jókòó síbẹ̀ ní àwọn ibùdó kan fún gbígbọ́ ọ̀rọ̀. Ṣùgbọ́n ẹni tó bá jọ́rọ̀ gbọ́ lásìkò yìí, ó máa rí ògúnná tó ti lúgọ dè é.",""
  72,10,"Dájúdájú àwa kò sì mọ̀ bóyá aburú ni wọ́n gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn tó wà lórí ilẹ̀ tàbí Olúwa wọn gbèrò ìmọ̀nà fún wọn.",""
  72,11,"Dájúdájú àwọn ẹni rere wà nínú wa. Àwọn mìíràn yàtọ̀ sí ìyẹn tún wà nínú wa. A wà lójú ọ̀nà (ẹ̀sìn) ọ̀tọ̀ọ̀tọ̀.",""
  72,12,"Dájúdájú àwa mọ àmọ̀dájú pé àwa kò lè mórí bọ́ mọ́ Allāhu lọ́wọ́ lórí ilẹ̀. Àwa kò sì lè sá mọ́ Ọn lọ́wọ́.",""
  72,13,"Dájúdájú nígbà tí a gbọ́ nípa ìmọ̀nà (láti inú al-Ƙur’ān), a gbà á gbọ́. Nítorí náà, ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo nínú Olúwa rẹ̀, kí ó má bẹ̀rù àdínkù(nínú ẹ̀san rere) àti (àlékún) aburú.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ìyẹn ni pé, wọn kò níí dín ẹ̀san iṣẹ́ rere onígbàgbọ́ òdodo kù, wọn kò sì níí fi kún àṣìṣe rẹ̀. Àti pé, àforíjìn Allāhu súnmọ́ ọn pẹ́kípẹ́kí lórí àwọn àṣìṣe náà."
